dcterms:description: A dataset containing human decisions made in a multi-stage game where human decision-makers interact with expert bots. The dataset includes 71,579 decisions made by 210 distinct human DMs, collected from May 2022 to November 2022.
dcterms:title: Human dataset

dcterms:creator: E. Shapira
R. Apel
M. Tennenholtz
R. Reichart
dcterms:description: A dataset generated by LLMs that replicates the human dataset collection process, where LLM-based players interact with the same set of experts and hotels. The dataset includes 430,610 decisions made by 4,134 LLM-based players.
dcterms:title: LLM dataset

dcterms:creator: E. Shapira
R. Apel
M. Tennenholtz
R. Reichart
dcterms:description: A dataset containing hotel reviews used in the human and LLM datasets, consisting of 1068 distinct hotels with reviews and scores.
dcterms:title: Hotel dataset
